item.description:
Happy Thanksgiving!!!

Today we look at (or for) Thanksgiving conspiracies, the we hop in the DeLorean to track down the ultimate time twister conspiracy: Is Donald Trump a time traveler?

Patreon
https://www.patreon.com/user?u=18482113

MERCH STORE!!!
https://tinyurl.com/y8zam4o2

Thanksgiving is a wonderful time of the year that’s full of lame ghosts, a surprising scarcity of crimes, and then we look at some odd Thanksgiving traditions.

Then we try to unravel the winding mystery that dares to ask the question: Is Donald Trump a time traveler?
